description: The fund is actively managed and invests in a combination of: U.S. Treasury securities; forwards, futures or options on various currencies; long and short positions on the short and long-end of the treasury or swap yield curve via futures, swaps, forwards and other over-the-counter (“OTC”) derivatives; long and short positions on equity indexes and/or investment companies, including ETFs; and commodity futures and options. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Advocate Rising Rate Hedge ETF
